select a.appointment_id, p.patient_id, d.doctor_id, p.givenName, p.familyName, d.dGivenName, d.dFamilyName, a.appointment_date, a.appointment_time, a.appointment_status, d.consultLink

:glucose,

);

create table patients (
  patient_id serial primary key, 
  bt_id varchar(7) CONSTRAINT bt_format CHECK (bt_id ~ '^[A-Z][0-9]{6}$'),
  n_id1 varchar(12), 
  n_id2 varchar(10) CONSTRAINT n_id2format check (n_id2 ~ '^[0-9]{9}[A-Z]$'),
  dob date, 
  givenname varchar, 
  familyname varchar, 
  contact int, 
  allergy jsonb, 
  immunisation jsonb, 
  familyhistory jsonb, 
  others jsonb
  );
SELECT patient_id, bt_id, givenname, familyname, gender, dob from patients

options.code:
const historyData = queries.createPatientHistory.data.map((a)=> {
  const d = `${a.appointment_date.split('T')[0]}T${a.appointment_time}`
  const da = `${a.appointment_date.split('T')[0]}`
  return {
    title: `${a.givenname} ${a.familyname}`,
    start: `${moment(d).format('MM-DD-YYYY HH:mm:ss A Z')}`,
    end: `${moment(d).add(0.5, 'hours').format('MM-DD-YYYY HH:mm:ss A Z')}`,
    allDay: false,
    tooltip: 'Patient Appointment',
    color: 'lightgreen',
    doctor:`${a.dgivenname} ${a.dfamilyname}`,
    aid:`${a.appointment_id}`,
    did: `${a.doctor_id}`, 
    diagnosis: `${a.diagnosis}`,
    preconsultation: a.preconsultation, 
    medication: a.medication,
    pid: `${a.patient_id}`,
    date: `${da}` 
}
}); 

actions.setVariable("history", historyData)
actions.unSetVariable('consaid ')

select a.appointment_id, p.patient_id, d.doctor_id, p.givenname, p.familyname, jsonb_agg(r.*) as precon
from appointments a 
  join patients p on a.patient_id = p.patient_id
  join doctor d on a.doctor_id = d.doctor_id
  join preconsultation r on r.appointment_id = a.appointment_id 
where a.appointment_id = :aid
GROUP BY a.appointment_id, p.patient_id, d.doctor_id, p.givenName, p.familyName, d.dGivenName, d.dfamilyname;

  start: `${moment(d).format('MM-DD-YYYY HH:mm:ss A Z')}`,

  meetLink: `${a.consultlink}`,

  status: `${a.appointment_status}`,
  pid: `${a.patient_id}`
}})
actions.setPageVariable('filterAppointment', filterAppointment);
